column2: "Ah, <%me>, do you have time to investigate something?"
"You can? Good, I just got here to Vopar."
"Once you're ready, we should meet up. See you when you get here."
"Does this mean you've decided to help me investigate?"
"Is it okay for you to trust me this easily?"
"I'm not part of ARKS. I've tried to gain your trust, but it could all be a ruse."
"You don't find it unsettling that I could betray you?"
"I don't know why I went off on that tangent."
"You can still neglect my request, it's up to you if you want to come or not."
"It would mean a lot to me if you came, but I'll leave that for you to decide."
